    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>If you have installed Google Toolbar for IE, may be you can face the same problem. Because, the toolbar capture the shortcut ctrl<kbd>+Space</kbd>.</p>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 743120,
